arCallbacks.szOnCallbackCompleteScript:
function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)
	------------------------------------------------------
	
	-- First Time Rewards
	
	local tAllPlayers = Hydra.QuestGetParticipants()
	
	for i, idPlayer in ipairs(tAllPlayers) do
		-- Drop the TreasureClass, which contains both "always" and "first time" rewards
		-- The First Time stuff is conditioned by the flag that is set after the drop occurs
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActorForPlayer(idActorKilled, "FirstTimeReward_Capstone_Elias", idPlayer)
		
		-- Set the variable, to mark that this player has recieved a reward
		Hydra.SetPlayerVariableFlag(idPlayer, "FirstTimeReward_Capstone_Elias")
	end
	
	------------------------------------------------------
end

function Start(sWorldName, sLevelAreaName)

	--Reset Music
	Hydra.ClearMusicOverride("CAP_Tier3_Step_FallenTemple")

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)
	
	-- Determine the Boss Encounter LevelArea dynamically
	S_HOLDOUT_LEVEL_AREA = Hydra.ActorGetLevelArea(idActorGizmo)
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyQueueStart(S_HOLDOUT_LEVEL_AREA)
	
	Holdout_DemonBarrier = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CAP_Tier3_Step_FallenTemple_Holdout_DemonBarrier")[1]
	Holdout_Demonwall = Hydra.ActorsInGroup("CAP_Tier3_Step_FallenTemple_Holdout_DemonWall")[1]
end

function Start(flTimeRemaining)
	
	local tSpawners = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(Holdout_DemonBarrier, "SPAWNERS")
	
	-- STOP SPAWNERS
	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(tSpawners) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, true)
		Hydra.ActorDisable(idSpawner)
	end
	
	Hydra.BossEncounterManuallyComplete(S_HOLDOUT_LEVEL_AREA)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(Holdout_Demonwall,2)
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(Holdout_DemonBarrier,1)

end

function Start(sWorldName, sLevelAreaName)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorReceptacle)

	local tplayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInParty(idActorPlayer)

	if #tplayers > 0 then
		
		for i, idplayer in ipairs(tplayers) do
			Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(DamageTakenDebuff,"Periodic_Debuff",idplayer)
		 end
	end
	
	Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(MainRoom_DemonBarrier,2)
end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

	for iter,idActor in pairs(Hydra.ActorsInGroup("DGN_Frac_AnicasClaim_QuestDoor")) do
		Hydra.ActorFadeAndDelete(idActor, 2)
	end

	local tplayers = Hydra.PlayerActorsInParty(idActorPlayer)

	if #tplayers > 0 then
		
		for i, idplayer in ipairs(tplayers) do
			Hydra.BuffRemove(CCIncreaseDebuff,"Periodic_Debuff",idplayer)
			Hydra.BuffRemove(DamageTakenDebuff,"Periodic_Debuff",idplayer)
		end
	end

end

function Start(idActor, fRange, idActorDetector)

	for i, idSpawner in ipairs(Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idActorDetector,"Monster")) do
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idSpawner, false)
	end

end
